description:
A look at internet claims that PCR testing for SARS-Cov-2 has a high failure rate.

If you'd like to support this channel, please donate to a charity I endorse: 
    https://healthinharmony.org/donate/
An explanation of their work can be found here:
   https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j9-GRugP9pU&t=1s

CORRECTIONS:
@10:19 I give the date of Lauritsen's article as 1998 - it should be 1996.
